query:
INSERT INTO candlestick (
                        codepoints,
                        start,
                        duration,
                        open,
                        close,
                        low,
                        high
                    ) VALUES (
                        $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7
                    )
                    ON CONFLICT (codepoints, duration, start)
                    DO UPDATE
                    SET
                        close = $5,
                        low = LEAST(candlestick.low, $6),
                        high = GREATEST(candlestick.high, $7)
